snippet.textDisplay: Had the opportunity to meet mac miller in 2013 and I passed up on it. Was dating a girl who knew him and we were in LA visiting some friends and he was having a party. I was a jealous kid and couldn’t get past the fact that she slept with him. I hadn’t really given his music a chance, and thought he was a douche based on his MTV show at the time. Got into his music a few years later and he’s had such a huge impact on me, especially in some of the darkest times of my life. I’ll always regret not going with her. That was an opportunity of a lifetime and I’ll certainly never get it again.
